org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.webapp.dao

Class ContainerLogsInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.webapp.dao.ContainerLogsInfo

  • public class ContainerLogsInfo
extends Object
    ContainerLogsInfo includes the log meta-data of containers.

    The container log meta-data includes details such as:

    • A list of ContainerLogFileInfo.
    • The container Id.
    • The NodeManager Id.
    • The logType: could be local or aggregated
